A vintage-style illustration of two massive filing cabinets facing each other across a cluttered desk, one painted in Gmail's red and white colors, the other in deep IBM blue. Between them, hundreds of paper envelopes and letters are frozen mid-flight, forming a swirling river of correspondence that flows from one cabinet to the other. The scene is rendered with warm sepia tones and aged paper textures, reminiscent of 1950s technical manuals. Small mechanical gears and clockwork mechanisms peek out from behind the cabinets, suggesting automated processes at work. The desk surface is scattered with coffee rings and pencil shavings, adding authentic lived-in character. Dramatic side lighting casts long shadows across the wooden floorboards beneath.
